      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just too much weight. i feel like i'm just existing, but there's nothing left to exist for. everyone's gonna look at me and just see a failure. a total zero. i'm already at the bottom, honestly. i might as well just stay here.",
